Financial Controller
Florence International Consulting
Dubai, UAE
Posted on: 29 Apr 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Florence International Consulting has a multinational client, based in the USA, that is looking for a new Financial Controller for the Dubai office in the UAE.
This client provides seismic services within the Oil and Gas industry and is one of the biggest Oil & Gas services company.
The Financial Controller needs to have a professional qualification in Finance along with some experience with companies that work in the Oil & Gas industry. They also need to have experience with international tax.
REQUIREMENTS
Requirements:
The successful Financial Controller will have the following:
- Minimum 7 years of experience as a Financial Controller in the Oil & Gas industry
- Bachelors in Finance
- Experience in International tax
- GCC Experience
If you meet the above mentioned criteria, please apply now online and you will be contacted by a specialist consultant from Florence International, Dubai.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Florence Consulting is a boutique search consultancy dedicated to introducing senior candidates within Finance and Accounting, Internal Audit and Human Resources.
Our International arm is head quartered in Dubai where we recruit across the Middle East with a particular focus on the UAE, Kuwait, Qatar and Saudi Arabia.
By combining our technical understanding and on the ground experience we offer a professional and personal service to both candidates and clients.
